# esy.com — Ecosystem Context

This is the ESY marketing and content site — the public-facing brand presence.

## Role

Consumer-facing marketing site at esy.com. Visual essays, brand storytelling, SEO content, documentation landing pages. This is NOT the app and NOT the API.

## Relationship to Other Repos

- `app.esy.com` is the dashboard app (control plane)
- `api.esy.com` is the Python API (execution plane)
- clip.art is ESY's primary consumer product
- ESY is engineer-first (see `docs/brand/ESY_DEFINITION.md` in this repo and `docs/strategy/sessions/2026-04-12-engineer-first-rebrand-and-homepage-redesign.md`)